headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Panic ProLaps Basketball Top and Shorts
content:
Show your team spirit: complete the Cayo Perico Heist Finale any time before March 17th to receive the Panic ProLaps Basketball Top; successfully stuff any Secondary Target into your Loot Bag by the 17th to get the Panic ProLaps Basketball Shorts.

Complete both in one fell swoop to earn the complete set and wear the full kit with pride.
